Assuming a constant mortality rate, from Eq. (10) it can be deduced that increasing the recovery rate will directly reduce the time span of the disease outbreak. However, there is a hard limit for the removal rate, \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
