The spatial features are only perturbated spatially and same values are copied temporally along the corresponding channel. The channels having temporal component are perturbated for different time slice within an input tensor. Each perturbated pixel in a time slice represents a separate feature. Input tensors are constructed using the perturbated values and passed through the blackbox model \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
